{{menutrail|Main menu}}
{{menutrail|Main menu|Game files menu}}
[[File:SaveGameMenu.png|thumb|The save game menu in [[Hordes of Chaos|HOCX]].]]The '''save game menu''' allows access to the list of [[savegame|saved games]] made from the played [[IWAD]]. Saves created with the same selection of mods are displayed in white; saves created with different mods are displayed in orange; either can be overwritten. Its [[MENUDEF]] name is {{c|SaveGameMenu}} and it can be summoned with the {{c|{{CCMD|O|menu_save}}}} console command.

Hitting the "delete" key allows to manually delete a saved game. ZDoom will ask you for confirmation before erasing the file.

Hitting the "N" key will automatically select the "new save" slot.
